main event: A civilian observed an unidentified object in West Hampton Beach, New York, on March 5, 1966.
interesting points: The document is part of Project Blue Book, which investigated UFO sightings., The sighting lasted between 2 to 3 minutes., The observation was made visually from the ground., The weather was reported as good with visibility of 15 miles., The object was described as having white lights and being in an oblong formation.
sighted object: an unidentified object with white lights in the sky
location: West Hampton Beach, New York, USA
witness description: a student who reported the sighting
